formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. Admin, General, Marketing & Selling Expenses are excluded while calculating Estimated Cost of Real Estate Project.
2. RERA carpet area is taken as given by the management/promoter developer.
3. Estimated Sale value -unit wise ( Excluding GST & Pass through charges) is taken as given by the management/promoter developer.
4. The promoter has repaid the loan of Rs. 30,00,00,000/- taken from Bajaj Housing Finance Limited and deed of reconveyance has been executed dated 5th May,2022. 
5. Further, the promoter has created second charge on the unsold shops and flats of the project in favour of Vistra ITCL (INDIA) Limited,Debenture Trustee, vide Mortgage Deed dated 2nd June,2020 to secure the Series A and Series B Debentures of amounting to Rs. 115,00,00,000 issued by Ratnaakar Infratech Private Limited, Wholly owned subsidiary of the promoter.
6. Further, the promoter has taken loan of Rs. 33,00,00,000/- from Motilal Oswal Home Finance Ltd , through Vistra ITCL (INDIA) Limited as Security Trustee vide simple mortgage deed dated 13th June,2022 by creating first ranking charge on Unsold Units as mentioned in the Mortgage Deed.
